      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though the suspension is a bit noisy over bumps and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle for someone looking for affordable transportation without the expectation of a perfect aesthetic.",
