      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards of care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to excellence. Mechanical performance is seamless, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a truly impeccable machine.",
