    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new car feel. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
